    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You bring yourself into a kind of artificial hibernation. Your pulse slows to an imperceptibly low pace, your body temperature starts to go down and you are @Condition[paralyzed]{paralyzed} while the technique lasts. In effect, you appear to be dead, though a Treat Injury check (DC 35) can reveal that you are merely pretending. You can dismiss the technique as a move action.</p>\n\n\n\n",
